{"tid":2268790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭卓堅司法覆核「限聚令」 批法例具政治目的打壓自由","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T06:45:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"58fbdfa130b48e27612f1da813d254dc38d3b034","tid":2268790,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅續指「限聚令」違反《基本法》第27條列明香港居民享有集會、遊行、示威的自由，認為整條法例具有政治目的。他又批評警察是選擇性執法，「從來無告過菲傭，排隊搭巴士、坐船又唔洗告！長洲成個碼頭（排隊隊伍）打曬圈無1.5米都唔告！」<br />\n<br />\n郭稱，若他成功「打倒」限聚令，「萬幾人唔洗交罰款」。他表示自己並沒有收到告票，但身邊有朋友收到五、六張；又指因為一直都沒有人司法覆核「限聚令」，自己才出手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078579&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=869844fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078579&h=42196569\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078579</a>"},{"pid":"87817f46a2b978ca5b2c044c02fe3d293e2ff7b1","tid":2268790,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">一直都沒有人司法覆核「限聚令」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊OMDB你個黨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b767524bf40ceba4ae49218ae77999c5932cbc7d","tid":2268790,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87817f46a2b978ca5b2c044c02fe3d293e2ff7b1","tid":2268790,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">一直都沒有人司法覆核「限聚令」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊OMDB你個黨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"打官司又唔去<br />\n又唔敢發死亡證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c